Client application to a Matrix server by Bamba William

This application allow you to : 

-log in
-Create rooms
-See the rooms you created 
-Send Messages 
-Show recent messages of the rooms 

npm install of the json package to install all dependencies .

Source : 

https://matrix.org/docs/spec/r0.0.0/client_server.html

https://scrimba.com/

https://colorlib.com/wp/

To create an user : 

An example :

In the terminal : 

curl -XPOST -d '{"username":"example", "password":"wordpass", "auth": {"type":"m.login.dummy"}}' "https://localhost:8448/_matrix/client/r0/register"

Username : test@github.com 
Password : password 

